Package semsim.annotation

Interface ReferenceTerm

All Known Implementing Classes:
PhysicalProperty, PhysicalPropertyInComposite, ReferencePhysicalDependency, ReferencePhysicalEntity, ReferencePhysicalProcess
public interface ReferenceTerm
Interface for physical model classes that are defined against controlled knowledge resource terms.
